<br>
Find Moltak (I'll describe where in a sec), kill him, camp/return, and go check faction on Solomen (I trust you can find him).<br>
<br>
To find Moltak...<br>
----------------------------------<br>
[1] start at Terblyn Zelbus (vends portal frags in Temp Sol Ro)<br>
[2] head South (away from him)<br>
[3] take a right at the corner<br>
[4] go to 2nd door on your left [LOC=+399, -18] <br>
[5] thru door (South), to intersection<br>
[6] left, then right at 1st door on right<br>
[7] South thru door to the seeker<br>
[8]  left (East) to next seeker<br>
[9] left (North) to door [LOC= +346,-33]<br>
 ==&gt;  thru door is Moltak<br>
<br>
Now, if I haven't totally screwed up the directions, you should be able to find Moltak and fix your faction.  (Geez, I hope he still does that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   )<br>
<br>
Killing Moltak doesn't aggro anyone, and when he repops, he isn't upset that you killed him, so go for it.<br>
